law.history: Repealed 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 156, sec. 4, effective June 17, 1954. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 153, sec. 4. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2054a-11, 2054a-16.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Expenditures, maximum amount permitted for county and district health departments.
